      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Product & Services

          h6 What is all about Product & Service offering ?
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="5" placeholder="Enter text here"

          h6.left Select offering Primary business : 
          select.left
            option Product

          h6 Product Name
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="2" placeholder="Enter text here"

          h6.left.small Product Type : 
          select.left.large
            option Software

          h6.left.small Product Subtype : 
          select.left.large
            option Enterprise

          h6 Product Description
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="2" placeholder="Enter text here"

          h6 Product Competative
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="2" placeholder="Enter text here"
      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Business Potential
          
          /Business model 
          h6.tag Business model 
          .content-business
            h6.left Type of Business model
            select.left
              option B2B
          .content-business
            h6.left.title-select Type of Business model
            select.left
              option Licencing, Subscription 
          h6 How this startup possess the business model ? 
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          h6 How much did you spend on the MVP? 
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"

          /Market Trend
          h6.tag style="background-color: #6CC6C4" Market Trend
          .content-business
            h6.left.large Market Trend - To what extent is your primary target market growing?
            select.left.small
              option Intermittent growth
          h6 Market Channels - How are you going to sell your product or service to potential customers? 
          p How this startup possess the business model ? 
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          .content-business
            h6.left.large Market Size - What is the total annual size of your primary target market ?
            select.left.small
              option $50M - $250M, $250M+
          h6 Describe the company's sales plan ?  
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          h6 Approx.Market share that your startup Possess ?  
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here"/
          
          /Customer Problem
          h6.tag style="background-color: #6CC6C4" Customer Problem
          h6 Does your startup solve a clearly defined customer problem in a (radically) new way? Explain ?  
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          .content-business.container-fluid
            h6.left.large What is the geographical region which you tragetting customers ?
            .right-select
              .select-element
                input type="checkbox"/
                span.input-checkbox
                select
                  option Intermittent growth
              .select-element
                input type="checkbox"/
                span.input-checkbox
                select
                  option NorthAmerica
              .select-element
                input type="checkbox"/
                span.input-checkbox
                select
                  option MiddleEast
          h6 Which age is startup business targetting ? 
          .age.container-fluid
            .age-element.container-fluid
              h6.left From Age
              select.left.small
                option 14 years
            .age-element.container-fluid
              h6.left To Age
              select.left.small
                option 45 years
          h6 Who are your potential competitors ?  
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          h6 Have you reached out to potential customers for feedback ?
          ul.radio-button
            li 
              input id="1" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="1" Yes
            li 
              input id="2" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="2" No

          / Competative Protection
          h6.tag style="background-color: #6FBEE1" Competative Protection
          h6 Describe the Startup's startegy for ongoing competative protection ?  
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="TextArea (here minimum 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
          .competator-section
            h6 Atleast one Competator should be added
            button 
              = image_tag 'icon-add.png'
              | Add Competators
            button View Competators
            button.btn-save Save
            .competator-content
              input type="text" placeholder="Enter Company Name"/
              input type="text" placeholder="Enter Their Primary Business Line"/
              input type="text" placeholder="Enter Country"/
              input type="text" placeholder="Enter Revenue (If know)"/
              input type="text" placeholder="Enter Website URL for reference"/
      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Financials

          h6 Your startup revenues stream measure in ? 
          select
            option Customer

          h6 How often the startup peforms accounting and finacial calculations ? 
          select
            option Monthly

          h6 Previous Year Revenue
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 Current Year Revenue
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 Previous Year NetProfit
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 Have you done crowdfunding ?
          ul.radio-button
            li 
              input id="1" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="1" Yes
            li 
              input id="2" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="2" No

          h6 Has an accelerator/incubator put money in startup?
          ul.radio-button
            li 
              input id="1" type="radio" name="2"/
              span for="1" Yes
            li 
              input id="2" type="radio" name="2"/
              span for="2" No

          h6 Upload your CurrentYear/Previous Financial year Balance Sheet document ?
          .custom-file-upload
            input type="file" id="file" name="myfiles[]"/
            span.sub-note 
              | (Add multiple docs: only PPT/DOC/PDF)

          h6 Upload your CurrentYear/Previous Financial year Cash Flow document ?
          .custom-file-upload
            input type="file" id="file" name="myfiles[]"/
            span.sub-note 
              | Add multiple docs: only PPT/DOC/PDF)

          h6 How much equity and debt has the company raised; what is the capitalization structure ?
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="3" placeholder="TextArea (here minium 100 characters and 600 maximum)"
      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Legal & Advisors

          h6 Has the startup employed the use of any professional advisors ?
          ul.radio-button
            li 
              input id="1" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="1" Yes
            li 
              input id="2" type="radio" name="1"/
              span for="2" No

          h6 Does the startup have a functioning board of advisors ?
          ul.radio-button
            li 
              input id="1" type="radio" name="2"/
              span for="1" Yes
            li 
              input id="2" type="radio" name="2"/
              span for="2" No

          h6 How many members are on the startup's board of advisors ? 
          select
            option Select Dropdown

          h6 How many hours of professional advice have been utilized by the company ? 
          select
            option Select Dropdown

          h6 How many members are on the company's board of directors / managers ? 
          select
            option Select Dropdown
      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Valuations

          h6 How many common and preferred shares or units are currently outstanding ?
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 How much total fund you startup raised so far ? 
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 How much total fund you startup raised so far ? 
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 How much and what type of capital is the startup currently seeking ? 
          select
            option Equity

          h6 Provide the company's estimated pre-money valuation
          input type="text" placeholder="Enter your text here (allow only numbers in $)"/

          h6 Offering business stake to the investor ? 
          select
            option Select Numbers 1-90(%)

          h6 How will you use these funds ?
          textarea# name="" cols="30" rows="3" placeholder="Enter text here"
      .profile.fund
        .profile-content.fund-content
          h3 Pitch Burns
          
          h6 Upload Startup Pitch Presentation
